line_1: Into that lower Space to enter,
line_2: Of the large Round, Her self the Center.

line_1: And courage undaunted advis'd me to enter,
line_2: I heard who was there, and was fearful to venture:

line_1: But in the House they durst not enter,
line_2: My Dame her Crock'ry would not venture;

line_1: Her hands were bloody — she would enter,
line_2: And, as I follow'd, to prevent her
